1. Vidimo se *naokolo*. (We'll see each other around.)
2. Da li se može proći *naokolo*? (Can we go around?)
3. *Naokolo* su bile samo livade. (There were only meadows around.)
4. Idemo *naokolo* kako bismo izbjegli gužvu. (We're going around to avoid the crowd.)
5. *Naokolo* je bilo mnogo drveća. (There was a lot of trees around.)
6. Moramo da prođemo *naokolo* kako bismo stigli do kafića. (We have to go around to get to the café.)
7. *Naokolo* se čulo samo cvrkut ptica. (Only the chirping of birds could be heard around.)
8. Ulica je zatvorena, moramo ići *naokolo*. (The street is closed, we have to go around.)
9. Nije bilo nikoga *naokolo* kada sam stigao. (There was no one around when I arrived.)
10. Skrenuli smo *naokolo* kako bismo obišli grad. (We turned around to tour the city.)